addOperation.body: @Operation changeCommonClass[monitor=false,delToClassAllowed=false](newCommonObject : XCore::String):XCore::Element let a = Clients::FmmlxDiagrams::FmmlxManipulator() then b = self.owner.classes->select(i | i.name.toString() = newCommonObject) in if (b <> null) then a.removeAssociationInstance(self.owner.getAssociation("refersToStateOf"),self,self.getCommonClass()); a.addAssociationInstance(self.owner,self,b.asSeq().at(0),self.owner.getAssociation("refersToStateOf")); if (self.getChilds() <> null) then @For child in self.getChilds() do child.checkCommonClass() end else false end else false end end end
addOperation.name: changeCommonClass

addOperation.body: @Operation checkCommonClass[monitor=false,delToClassAllowed=false]():XCore::Element let a = self.getControlElements()->select(i | i.of().name.toString() = "ListInjection") in if (not a->isEmpty) then if (a.asSeq().at(0).getInstanceList().contains(self.getCommonClass())) then true else self.changeCommonClass(a.asSeq().at(0).getInstanceList().at(0).name.toString()) end else self.changeCommonClass(self.owner.getLinkEnds(self.getParent().getCommonClass(),self.getAssociation().name).asSeq().at(0).name.toString()) end ; if (self.getChilds() <> null) then @For child in self.getChilds() do child.checkCommonClass() end else false end end end
addOperation.name: checkCommonClass

addOperation.body: @Operation getAssociation[monitor=false,delToClassAllowed=false]():Associations::Association if (self.associationName <> "") then self.owner.associations.asSeq()->select(i | i.name.toString() = self.associationName).at(0) else false end end
addOperation.name: getAssociation

addOperation.body: @Operation getInjection[monitor=true,delToClassAllowed=false]():XCore::Element if self.of().name().toString() = "SlotInjection" then self.getSlotValue() elseif self.of().name().toString() = "ActionInjection" then self.getOperationValue() elseif self.of().name().toString() = "ListInjection" then self.getInstanceNamesList() else false end end
addOperation.name: getInjection

addOperation.body: @Operation getInstanceByID[monitor=false,delToClassAllowed=false](idUI : XCore::String):ControllerMapping::UIElement self.of().parents->select(i | i.name.toString() = "UIElement").asSeq().at(0)->allInstances->collect(i | i.allInstances())->flatten->select(i | i.idOfUIElement = idUI) end
addOperation.name: getInstanceByID

addOperation.body: @Operation getInstanceList[monitor=true,delToClassAllowed=false]():XCore::Seq(ControllerMapping::CommonClass) let a = Seq{}; b = self.getReference(); c = self.owner in if (b.isHead) then b.getCommonClass().of().allInstances()->select(i | true).asSeq() else b.getCommonClass().of().allInstances()->select(i | c.hasAssociationInstance(b.getParent().getCommonClass(),i,b.getAssociation())).asSeq() end end end
addOperation.name: getInstanceList

addOperation.body: @Operation invoiceTotal[monitor=true,delToClassAllowed=false]():XCore::Float self.getInvoiceItems()->iterate(i sum = 0 | sum := sum + i.calcPrice()) end
